trans-unit.source: The exception that is thrown when an XML document cannot be deserialized into a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref> by a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A exceção que é lançada quando um documento XML não pode ser desserializado em um <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"> </xref> por um <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> throws this exception it supplies a message that describes the reason for the exception.

trans-unit.source: In some cases the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> supplies a list of validation errors and warnings that it encountered while trying to deserialize the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>.

trans-unit.source: An exception that is thrown as a direct result of a previous exception should include a reference to the previous exception in the <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Uma exceção que é lançada como um resultado direto de uma exceção anterior deve incluir uma referência à exceção anterior no <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property returns the same value that is supplied to the constructor or a null reference (Nothing in Visual Basic) if the `innerException` parameter does not supply the inner exception value to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>propriedade retorna o mesmo valor que é fornecido para o construtor ou uma referência nula (Nothing no Visual Basic) se o `innerException` parâmetro não fornecer o valor da exceção interna para o construtor.</xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> object with the collection of <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.ValidationEventArgs"></xref> associated with this exception, and additional exception information.

trans-unit.source: GetObjectData sets a <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo> with all the exception object data targeted for serialization.
trans-unit.target: GetObjectData define um <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>com todos os dados do objeto de exceção destinados para a serialização.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>

trans-unit.source: During deserialization the exception object is reconstituted from the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo> transmitted over the stream.
trans-unit.target: Durante a desserialização do objeto de exceção é reconstituído do <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>transmitido no fluxo.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>

trans-unit.source: For more information see XML and SOAP Serialization.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte serialização SOAP e XML.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> that holds the serialized object data about the exception being thrown.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> que contém os dados do objeto serializado sobre a exceção que está sendo gerada.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext> that contains contextual information about the source or destination.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>que contém informações contextuais sobre a origem ou destino.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>

trans-unit.target: infoé uma referência nula ( no Visual Basic)

trans-unit.source: Gets a list that contains validation warnings and errors associated with this exception.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma lista que contém os avisos de validação e erros associados a essa exceção.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> uses an <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> to deserialize an XML document into a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>usa um <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>desserializar um documento XML em <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> collects validation errors and warnings emitted by the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>coleta de erros de validação e os avisos emitidos pelo <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>.</xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>

trans-unit.source: At certain points during deserialization, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> determines whether the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> has encountered any validation errors, and, if it has, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> adds these warnings and errors to ValidationEventArgs and throws a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileDeserializationException>.
trans-unit.target: Em determinados pontos durante a desserialização, o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>determina se o <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>encontrou erros de validação e, em caso afirmativo, o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>adiciona esses avisos e erros ValidationEventArgs e lança um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileDeserializationException>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileDeserializationException> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> </xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>

trans-unit.source: Not all exceptions of this class will have ValidationEventArgs set.
trans-unit.target: Nem todas as exceções desta classe terão o conjunto de ValidationEventArgs.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.IList> of <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.ValidationEventArgs"></xref> objects that contains validation warnings and errors associated with this exception.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Collections.IList>de <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.ValidationEventArgs"> </xref> objetos que contém os avisos de validação e erros associados a essa exceção.</xref:System.Collections.IList>

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty list.
trans-unit.target: O padrão é uma lista vazia.
